com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.plate

Class WellList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.plate.WellList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<WellList>, Iterable<WellIndex>

    public class WellList
extends Object
implements Iterable<WellIndex>, Comparable<WellList>
    Internal data structure to hold lists of well indices for well sets or plates. The list of well indices prevents redundant data storage for the wells within a well set or plate object.
    Author:
    Jesse L. Mull
